168
00:14:55,040 --> 00:14:57,200
<font backgroundcolor="#000000"> A jak smakuje? </font>

169
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:59,440
<font backgroundcolor="#000000"> Jadłem wczoraj. </font>

170
00:14:59,640 --> 00:15:01,600
<font backgroundcolor="#000000"> Skrobia. </font>

171
00:15:01,760 --> 00:15:05,120
<font backgroundcolor="#000000"> Bez soli, bez dodatków. Bez sosiku. </font>

172
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:07,880
